1
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,680
Brother.

2
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,780
What are you doing?

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,730
The shower in my room is broken,

4
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:26,960
so I came to use yours.

5
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,880
As for Miss Yao,

6
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:30,360
I have no idea.

7
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:32,840
Huainan, I came to see you.

8
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,880
I wanted to see your room

9
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,480
to get to know my fiancé better.

10
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:37,280
Oh, my.

11
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,800
Isn't this Miss Yao?

12
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:42,960
Why are you with Qingzhou?

13
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:43,920
Well...

14
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,120
Soon,

15
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:48,800
the new mistress of the Song family will be moving in.

16
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,960
Don't act like you used to.

17
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:52,090
You must learn the rules of this house.

18
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:53,570
Understood.

19
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,520
Mistress.

20
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,560
Make way.

21
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:06,480
Miss Yao, you haven't married into the family yet.

22
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:08,280
They are guests here, after all.

23
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,640
This isn't proper etiquette.

24
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,560
Then what kind of hospitality

25
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:14,400
is the Song family showing?

26
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:18,240
Huainan, you trust me, don't you?

27
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,200
You're my future wife.

28
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:21,880
Of course I trust you.

29
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:24,760
Huainan.

30
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,680
Enough, Stepmother.

31
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,800
Let's drop this.

32
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,120
You may leave.

33
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,579
How long are you going to hold onto me?

34
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,440
Yao Shengsheng, this is a military building.

35
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,840
You can't just come here whenever you want.

36
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,440
I'm here to see my fiancé

37
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,200
to bond with him.

38
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,780
Do I need your permission?

39
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,520
I'm sorry, Miss Yao.

40
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,520
Entering this building

41
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,320
does indeed require my approval.

42
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,040
Besides,

43
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,680
there is a dress code.

44
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:57,240
No high heels.

45
00:02:57,920 --> 00:03:00,240
You can't wear your hair down.

46
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,840
And you're not wearing formal attire.

47
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,450
I'm sorry, Miss Yao.

48
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,160
You don't pass.

49
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,480
Come on.

50
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,280
Look.

51
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,000
Make an exception.

52
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,240
Qingzhou.

53
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:27,920
Brother.

54
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:38,040
I received a request from Uncle Yao this morning.

55
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,440
He said you want to be my secretary

56
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,770
to get to know me better.

57
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,400
Since you didn't refuse,

58
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,660
I'll take that as a yes.

59
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,920
What makes you think

60
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,520
you can handle this job?

61
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,000
What makes you think I can't?

62
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,460
This isn't playing house.

63
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,120
If you want to be my secretary,

64
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,360
then prove it to me.

65
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,360
And you.

66
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:57,180
Messing around in the military academy.

67
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,720
Miss Yao has been very forward lately.

68
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,920
Now she wants to come to our academy

69
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,640
to be your personal secretary.

70
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,160
Could this be a setup by the Yao family?

71
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,019
A smokescreen?

72
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,120
Do you want me to investigate?

73
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,680
No need.

74
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,680
She is just a wealthy young lady.

75
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,400
She will leave once she has had her fun.

76
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,000
You are dismissed.

77
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,530
Yes, sir.

78
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,090
Brother.

79
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,200
Go ahead.

80
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,880
How do you plan to test me?

81
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,240
Strip.

82
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,400
Strip searches are usually for men.

83
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,800
Isn't it a bit inappropriate for a woman?

84
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,960
To be my secretary,

85
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,240
loyalty is the primary condition.

86
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,000
I need absolute obedience,

87
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,700
regardless of gender.

88
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,440
Strip.

89
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,500
That's enough.

90
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,760
Didn't I just say that's enough?

91
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,000
Men and women are equal.

92
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,800
I don't need special treatment.

93
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,880
How was it? Did I pass?

94
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,600
To work here,

95
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,520
you still need some fitness

96
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,050
and competitive training.

97
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:30,920
No.

98
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,080
Why can't I?

99
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,120
Whatever Song Qingzhou and the others do,

100
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,960
I can do it too.

101
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,560
I hope you can hold on.

102
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,050
He isn't trying to test you.

103
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,650
He wants you to back off.

104
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:15,440
Song Huainan takes this road every day.

105
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,380
Hey, gorgeous.

106
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,940
It's getting late.

107
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,680
Why are you out here all alone?

108
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,410
Do you want me

109
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,320
to walk you home?

110
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,200
Boss,

111
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,760
are you all right?

112
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,680
Who are you?

113
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,140
Meddling in our business?

114
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,880
Let's go, Boss. Forget it.

115
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,409
Let's go.

116
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,530
Are you okay?

117
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,450
I'm fine.

118
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,370
Thank you for saving me.

119
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,660
Why are you out here

120
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,640
alone so late?

121
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,480
I sprained my ankle.
